http://www.sohu.com/a/420027203_191631	12044
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/6cf96fd68f02430e8105e068f51206a4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中央美术学院是所有艺考生梦寐以求的艺术殿堂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但很多学生望而却步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么今天这篇文章告诉你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">离中央美院最近的地方在哪里!</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/c622d0f2f3cc42d982780868024ac27b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200922/554bdbc6dd044a43a38cc5f887b4884c.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
